{"tid":1417744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停停停,你地重溫多次元朗黑夜先啦","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:19:32.000Z","uid":266924,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"154110745b3eba85e574720d758cad767b98205d","tid":1417744,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D16CiwPChpr0&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=5faf79ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0</a><br />\n香港人為左大眾利益,香港福祉挺身對抗暴政<br />\n眼見警察同黑社會有糾纏不清既關係,義理永遠都係市民一方<br />\n點會仲有人動搖,點會仲有人善忘<br />\n示威者已經係名正言順,敵人唔同你講仁義道德,反而有風向要和理非,同前線割蓆,你地係唔係食左懵仔丸呀<br />\n唔該大家企穩陣腳,唔好咁易俾人搖倒啦<br />\n再重申今次係長期抗爭,唔好因為閒言閒語而改變立場<br />\n大家專注一樣野就夠,就係為香港前途奮鬥<br />\n同路人之間永不分化,不割蓆!"},{"pid":"9a8bee2b3eca74578da67b6d9f383e4b7502416c","tid":1417744,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73f3e71b5c137f2544eb31353ee45241b66ef098","tid":1417744,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb0e9200740e1017b432333977626d81b4cc4df3","tid":1417744,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"467b15c8d09b3367b46f99409ddeead53d927722","tid":1417744,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80fd3980e1f725de8a585182132037248401d2aa","tid":1417744,"uid":285536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 核爆都唔割<br />\n<br />\n對準警黑政權不分化！！"},{"pid":"bf471a43882402da894095eb3b2d92572cd0033e","tid":1417744,"uid":165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 核爆都唔割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces